text: Didier Garcia (born 23 May 1964) is a French former cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit and the points race events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Blanc-Mesnil Category:French track cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Seine-Maritime
